					<h2>Open Hack(Hack Fest)</h2> 
					<p>A hack day is an event where developers, designers and people with ideas gather to build <mark>'cool stuff'</mark> - the events now run all over the world and are organised by <em>Yahoo!</em> as well as other organisations such as the <em>BBC</em>, <em>Lonely Planet</em> and even government departments across the world.</p> 
					<h3>Benefits</h3>
					<p>Innovation on the fly.</p>
					<p>Get down to work and produce 3 months worth of work in 24hrs. Tested and proven.</p>
					<p>Companies are seeing real productivity with internal hack days.</p>
					<p><%= link_to image_tag("register_now_free.png", :alt => "Registration is free" ), "//www.meetup.com/iLinkoln/events/17555476/", :title => "Register now for free", :target => "_blank" %></p>
